 given name dates from the 19th century, when it is also recorded occasionally as a boy's name in the United States. In some instances the given name may be a transferred use of the surname derived in the medieval period from the vocabulary word."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Elen ferch Maredudd was born about 1270, in Llanbadarn fawr, Cardiganshire, Wales, her father, Maredudd ap Cadwgon, was 42 and her mother, Gwenllian de Deuheubarth, was 30. She had at least 1 son and 2 daughters with Maredudd Fychan ap Maredudd. She died after 1332."},"et":{"about 1270–after 1332":"umbes 1270–pärast 1332","1260–1332":"1260–1332","1265–Female":"1265–Surnud","1270–1332":"1270–1332","1260–Male":"1260–Surnud","1286–Male":"1286–Surnud","1290–Female":"1290–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1230–Male":"1230–Surnud","1242–Female":"1242–Surnud","about 1270":"umbes 1270","ABT    1286":"umbes 1286","1332":"1332","1265":"1265","1242":"1242","1286":"1286","1230":"1230","ABT    1290":"umbes 1290","1260":"1260","after 1332":"pärast 1332","1270":"1270","1290":"1290","of,Derllys cmt,Carmarthenshire,Wales":"Carmarthenshire, Wales, United Kingdom","Llanbadarn fawr, Cardiganshire, Wales":"Llanbadarn fawr, Cardiganshire, Wales"},"fi":{"about 1270–after 1332":"noin 1270–1332 jälkeen","1260–1332":"1260–1332","1265–Female":"1265–Kuollut","1270–1332":"1270–1332","1260–Male":"1260–Kuollut","1286–Male":"1286–Kuollut","1290–Female":"1290–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1230–Male":"1230–Kuollut","1242–Female":"1242–Kuollut","about 1270":"noin 1270","ABT    1286":"noin 1286","1332":"1332","1265":"1265","1242":"1242","1286":"1286","1230":"1230","ABT    1290":"noin 1290","1260":"1260","after 1332":"1332 jälkeen","1270":"1270","1290":"1290","of,Derllys cmt,Carmarthenshire,Wales":"Carmarthenshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Llanbadarn fawr, Cardiganshire, Wales":"Llanbadarn fawr, Cardiganshire, Wales"},"fr":{"about 1270–after 1332":"environ 1270–après 1332","1260–1332":"1260–1332","1265–Female":"1265–Décédée","1270–